title: Delphine Linux Bundle
description:
Delphine Linux Bundle - Another World/Flashback/Fade To Black

All games comes packed with all data files and binaries for x86 and x86_64.
These are older builds but they still work on most latest distros.
Source is included for all games, so don't whine if something doesn't work, just compile it yourself.

If You have a problem with Another World on x86_64, start the game with command "linux32 ./aw". There is also a "Code Wheel" in "extra" directory for Another World, or you can just press CTRL+L to load saved position and skip the wheel.
